# Pedagogical Presence
## Definition
The capacity of an educator to devote sustained attention, preparation, and authentic engagement to teaching and learning.
## Context
Pedagogical Presence represents the principal objective of the Educator Intelligence Platform. Every architectural decision should ultimately contribute to increasing an educator's presence with students.
## Design Implications
Features should be evaluated according to whether they increase or diminish pedagogical presence.
